.TH "FACADE-SSH" "8" "" "Project Kennel" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
facade\-ssh \- in\-kennel SSH egress connector
.SH SYNOPSIS
(internal \(em forked by kenneld(8), not invoked directly)
.SH DESCRIPTION
facade\-ssh is the in\-kennel connector for per\-kennel SSH egress. The kennel never holds a real key; this process reaches the re\-origination bastion, which runs the host\-side ssh as the operator against a destination fixed by which synthetic key authenticated.
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBkenneld\fR(8), \fBkennel\fR(1)
